                            <comment id="14552817" author="mchung" created="Thu, 19 Jan 2023 10:56:31 -0800"  >As noted in the comment of VarHandles.getStaticFieldFromBaseAndOffset, it&amp;#39;s fragile to assume the base is the receiver type.   This can be fixed by having VarHandle implementation for static fields to include the class in addition to the base and offset (i.e. FieldStaticReadOnly and FieldStaticReadWrite classes).&lt;br/&gt;
